snippet.title: Team Sonic Racing OST - "Haunted Castle"
snippet.description: Tee Lopes and Jun Senoue combine forces for this ghoulishly-good song, with special violin performance by Tei Sena! It may not be Halloween yet, but what’s not to love about a Haunted Castle?
